{"tid":2334212,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《香港年報2019》證實721事件 係「一群人在元朗站襲擊示威者和乘客」","createTime":"2020-12-21T04:37:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-21T07:14:08.000Z","uid":22556,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e8251db651340a60f8f3379622bb5930ff37b41c","tid":2334212,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T04:37:17.000Z","msg":"元朗7.21白衣人恐襲案中「原告變被告」的民主黨副主席林卓廷，明天再次上庭應訊，他今晚 （20日）在Facebook直播中稱，政府新聞處強調「經多方核證、力求準確無誤」才出版的《香港年報2019》中「大事紀要」一章，談及去年元朗7.21事件時，描述為「一群人在元朗站襲擊示威者和乘客」<br />\n<br />\n林認為，上述官方紀錄如「食咗誠實豆沙包、記載咗史實」，質疑政府由於受到北京政府壓力才決定扭曲7.21事實，並在明知理虧下仍控告他和其他在場巿民參與7.21暴動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201220/WTH6N5WUVNBHBF4NDPUJOZYXQE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2hyEJKorQVIE14u_qhfx_gks8a8DD5VovPvL_Afg2E0NzjryBVcTUXQo8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201220%2FWTH6N5WUVNBHBF4NDPUJOZYXQE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2hyEJKorQVIE14u_qhfx_gks8a8DD5VovPvL_Afg2E0NzjryBVcTUXQo8&d=Yr0hxYoWOJ9ZaoTMuy4WzNOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=45de1811\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201220%2FWTH6N5WUVNBHBF4NDPUJOZYXQE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2hyEJKorQVIE14u_qhfx_gks8a8DD5VovPvL_Afg2E0NzjryBVcTUXQo8&h=8d8d26af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201220/WTH6N5WUVNBHBF4NDPUJOZYXQE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2hyEJKorQVIE14u_qhfx_gks8a8DD5VovPvL_Afg2E0NzjryBVcTUXQo8</a>"},{"pid":"e9bd3ada83f8c30208a01e2a2923e5ba4f61c84e","tid":2334212,"uid":306614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score"